WEBVTT

00:00:29.864 --> 00:00:34.263
But why is the question always
do they love us?

00:00:34.287 --> 00:00:36.398
Why is it always about us?

00:00:36.422 --> 00:00:39.065
Why are we such narcissists?

00:00:40.674 --> 00:00:43.713
I found a different question
to ask animals.

00:00:45.911 --> 00:00:47.328
Who are you?

00:00:49.910 --> 00:00:52.805
There are capacities of the human mind

00:00:52.829 --> 00:00:57.691
that we tend to think are capacities
only of the human mind.

00:00:58.176 --> 00:00:59.534
But is that true?